Usage: getPinConstraint [-help] [-dictFile <string>] [[-global  | -cell <cell_name>] [-global  | -pin <pin_name_list>]]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-cell <cell_name>                        # Specifies the name of the cell,
                                         # wildcard can be specified. The cell
                                         # name is not required if the command
                                         # is run on a top-level cell.
                                         # (string, optional)
-dictFile <string>                       # dump equivalent TCL dictionary in
                                         # the specified file (string, optional)
-global                                  # Specifies to get global constraints.
                                         # (bool, optional)
-pin <pin_name_list>                     # Specifies the name of the partition
                                         # pin. You can use wildcards with this
                                         # parameter. (string, optional)